{"tid":155280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家上連登咁耐，有無唸過中聯辦可能已經Hack左呢到Server","createTime":"2017-03-14T01:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T04:44:36.000Z","uid":88032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee01f2f3f95ec71f5de85871944e88671b7bd7f","tid":155280,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"睇左些少Wikileaks放出黎既CIA Hacking Tools：<br />\n<a href=\"https://wikileaks.org/ciav7p1/cms/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwikileaks.org%2Fciav7p1%2Fcms%2Findex.html&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6c4e73ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://wikileaks.org/ciav7p1/cms/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n裡便Hack人既方法，俄羅斯同大陸既特工有用到係一D都唔出奇。<br />\n<br />\n以前高登就有暗通中聯辦將會員資料過比大陸，但而家就算連登既Firewall可能好勁，中聯辦都有機會經過ISP去攞到會員資料，又或者已經Hack左連登，都唔出奇。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦手上面會唔會好似CIA咁，已經有張Watch List，等到23條一到，就馬上動刀？<br />\n<br />\n連登貌似好安全，但Hacking Tools如果係Comprehensive，大家用緊既咁多電子產品又有咁多Backdoor / Bug，會唔會只不過係大家自以為安全而FF打緊飛機？"},{"pid":"66138b8347017067c96c99c65e357da75faacc31","tid":155280,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:39:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天滅中共</span></span>"},{"pid":"32d9867a3b462b08a94dbe8ee25a702618e1ff35","tid":155280,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天滅中共</span></span></blockquote><br />\n攞我資料啦!"},{"pid":"9bea38e31d52dacc6378daabd02309a58e05d146","tid":155280,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"與其懷疑連登俾人hack, 不如望下自己部小米router, 手提啦"},{"pid":"b115d8ed660d8d496a21a2e8fc74b58ab9f3ffab","tid":155280,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHack都唔洗直接攞資料"},{"pid":"6ed6322e1849c6acbfd7132ba7e982e88a50fc87","tid":155280,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:30:45.000Z","msg":"而家好多人都用華為Server，貪平<br />\n其實好撚危險<br />\n就算自己唔用，ISP縮數要用，都死人<br />\n同埋而家唔止中聯通同中移動，中電訊都黎緊香港插旗<br />\n<br />\nBig brother is watching you"},{"pid":"654c2d40b471da3d92563f33e2b6886a770c43ba","tid":155280,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"廿三條立左法，佢唔洗hack你啦<br />\n直接要法庭出柯打要連尼住交人"},{"pid":"8dee91c6ad7916c559ca08db28a43500aaff670d","tid":155280,"uid":12438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"咪又係得個知字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fad33e906ab95412e249ed165cc66cc598c95e","tid":155280,"uid":62743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"其實最好就學日本玩暱名留言版/BBS 你要isp注冊 個下已經死左"},{"pid":"4ef871e7ff9c6da9f9c99c5029281e48eadc088b","tid":155280,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實最好就學日本玩暱名留言版/BBS 你要isp注冊 個下已經死左</blockquote><br />\nkomica"}]}